    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not the same thing as \"change\" though. it's not like i'm starting a new chapter or anything. the version of me that actually mattered is dead. the person people respected, the person who had a purpose... that person doesn't exist anymore. i'm just a shell of a person walking through a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. it feels like i'm just performing being alive.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
